name: Furniture_of_America_Tobiath_Rustic_Dark_Oak_Dining_Table
reviews: This table is solid and very well made. Its gift a beautiful warm color and finish. We couldn't be happier with this purchase. I would buy again from Furniture of America...very pleased.
